### 获得凭证列表分页 /admin-api/system/platforminfo/simple-simple
GET {{baseUrl}}/system/license/page?pageNum=1&pageSize=2
Authorization: Bearer e9f2faef4dfb48169fc69e1ac7aeefdb

### 导出凭证
GET {{baseUrl}}/system/license/export?id=545790779306676224
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

### 上传凭证
POST {{baseUrl}}/system/license/import
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="license.lic.sm4"
Content-Type: application/octet-stream

< ./license.lic-1.sm4
--WebAppBoundary--